buildnotify for Debian
----------------------

buildnotify is designed to be started when logging in. This can be acheived by
by using the 'Startup Applications' dialog or by creating a .desktop in 
~/.config/autostart/ 

An example .desktop file can be found in /usr/share/doc/buildnotify/examples

